{"id": "23873", "post": "<div class=\"post-23873 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-tutorials tag-2fa tag-security tag-tutorial tag-web tag-wordpress\" id=\"post-23873\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/shields-up-protecting-your-wordpress-site-with-wordfence/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Shields Up! Protecting Your WordPress Site with Wordfence</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/2fa/\" rel=\"tag\">2FA</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/security/\" rel=\"tag\">Security</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/tutorial/\" rel=\"tag\">tutorial</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/web/\" rel=\"tag\">web</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/wordpress/\" rel=\"tag\">wordpress</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \"> October 3, 2020 @ 7:42 am, by raindog308</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIyNzEiIGhlaWdodD0iNzAiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCAyNzEgNzAiPjxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSIxMDAlIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEwMCUiIGZpbGw9IiNjZmQ0ZGIiLz48L3N2Zz4=\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"screenshot\" title=\"Shields Up! Protecting Your WordPress Site with Wordfence\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/lowendtutorial.png.webp\" alt=\"Shields Up! Protecting Your WordPress Site with Wordfence\" width=\"271\" height=\"70\"></a>Server and application security are important factors to consider when running a website \u2014 especially a website based on WordPress. This easy to use guide will help take you through the steps of ensuring that your WordPress based blog is running as securely as possible thanks to Wordfence (and easy to use plugin that goes a long way to towards improving security on your WordPress installation).</p><p>Wordfence is a Web Application Firewall that can substantially improve the security of your WordPress site.&nbsp; It\u2019s a WP plugin and can be managed entirely through your WordPress dashboard.&nbsp; In this tutorial, we\u2019ll get you up and running with Wordfence.</p><p><span id=\"more-23873\"></span></p><h1>Installing Wordfence</h1><p>I\u2019ve created a blog with absorbing content and wish to protect it from hackers.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iMTEwNiIgdmlld0JveD0iMCAwIDgwMCAxMTA2Ij48cmVjdCB3aWR0aD0iMTAwJSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxMDAlIiBmaWxsPSIjY2ZkNGRiIi8+PC9zdmc+\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23874\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-1.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"1106\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-1.png.webp 800w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-1-217x300.png.webp 217w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-1-741x1024.png.webp 741w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-1-768x1062.png.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></p><p>I\u2019ll head to my dashboard and click Plugins, then Add New.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iMzkyIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNTAwIDM5MiI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23875\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-2.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"392\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-2.png.webp 500w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-2-300x235.png.webp 300w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"></p><p>In the search box, enter \u201cwordfence\u201d.&nbsp; Under \u201cWordfence Security \u2013 Firewall &amp; Malware Scan\u201d click \u201cInstall Now\u201d.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNDgzIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgODAwIDQ4MyI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23876\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-3.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"483\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-3.png.webp 800w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-3-300x181.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-3-768x464.png.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></p><p>The installer will spin for a few seconds as it installs.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iMzc1IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNTAwIDM3NSI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23877\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-4.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-4.png.webp 500w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-4-300x225.png.webp 300w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"></p><p>When it\u2019s done, click Activate.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iMzc3IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNTAwIDM3NyI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23878\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-5.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"377\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-5.png.webp 500w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-5-300x226.png.webp 300w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"></p><p>Congrats, Wordfence is installed.&nbsp; You\u2019ll be greeted with a success message.&nbsp; One of the options is to subscribe to their security alerts email list.&nbsp; I recommend subscribing, as their emails discuss current WordPress attack patterns.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNDk0IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgODAwIDQ5NCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23879\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-6.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"494\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-6.png.webp 800w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-6-300x185.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-6-768x474.png.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></p><p>Wordfence offers a premium mode.&nbsp; In this tutorial, we won\u2019t be covering that option, so just click \u201cNo Thanks\u201d.&nbsp; One of the nice things about Wordfence is that the product provides a lot of benefits even without paying for premium.&nbsp; You\u2019ll occasionally run into things that are premium-only that maybe you wish you had, but even as a freebie, Wordfence is very beneficial.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNDU1IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgODAwIDQ1NSI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23880\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-7.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"455\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-7.png.webp 800w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-7-300x171.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-7-768x437.png.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></p><h1>Configuring Wordfence</h1><p>On your dashboard\u2019s left menu bar, you\u2019ll now see a Wordfence section.&nbsp; Click it.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxNDQiIGhlaWdodD0iNTAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMTQ0IDUwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23881\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-8.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"144\" height=\"500\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-8.png.webp 144w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-8-86x300.png.webp 86w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 144px) 100vw, 144px\"></p><p>Wordfence has a few tutorial-like popups that will orient you.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iMzEyIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgODAwIDMxMiI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23882\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-9.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"312\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-9.png.webp 800w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-9-300x117.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-9-768x300.png.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></p><p>At the top of the Wordfence dashboard, you\u2019ll see this option.&nbsp; Click \u201cYes\u201d so Wordfence can stay up to date.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNzMiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCA4MDAgNzMiPjxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSIxMDAlIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEwMCUiIGZpbGw9IiNjZmQ0ZGIiLz48L3N2Zz4=\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23883\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-10.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"73\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-10.png.webp 800w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-10-300x27.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-10-768x70.png.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></p><p>Next, click on the orange tab to optimize your Wordfence wAF.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iMTE1IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgODAwIDExNSI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23884\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-11.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"115\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-11.png.webp 800w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-11-300x43.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-11-768x110.png.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></p><p>What this is actually going to do is prepend a call to a .php file before every php call WordPress makes.&nbsp; Click Continue.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNDgxIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgODAwIDQ4MSI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23885\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-12.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"481\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-12.png.webp 800w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-12-300x180.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-12-768x462.png.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></p><p>If you\u2019re curious, the file modified is .user.ini in your WordPress root.&nbsp; Here is the modification made:</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iODUiIHZpZXdCb3g9IjAgMCA4MDAgODUiPjxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSIxMDAlIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjEwMCUiIGZpbGw9IiNjZmQ0ZGIiLz48L3N2Zz4=\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23888\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-15.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"85\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-15.png.webp 800w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-15-300x32.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-15-768x82.png.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></p><p>You\u2019ll notice that Wordfence says its in \u201cLearning Mode\u201d.&nbsp; The WF engine is being tuned for your site and it\u2019s learning what typical access patterns users use.&nbsp; Typically you leave it in \u201cLearning Mode\u201d for a period of time (one week) before it moves into active mode.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iODU4IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgODAwIDg1OCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23892\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-18.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"858\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-18.png.webp 800w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-18-280x300.png.webp 280w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-18-768x824.png.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></p><p>Let\u2019s look at some of the ways Wordfence is already protecting your site.&nbsp; Still on the Firewall page, click All Firewall Options.&nbsp; WordPress has put some generous defaults in place to protect you against people trying to guess passwords.&nbsp; Note also that WF prevents the use of passwords that have appeared in data breaches.&nbsp; This is a fantastic improvement.&nbsp; You and your admins are prevented from using passwords that are in well-known password databases.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjI1IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgODAwIDYyNSI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23890\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-17.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"625\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-17.png.webp 800w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-17-300x234.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-17-768x600.png.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></p><p>Scrolling down, you\u2019ll see Wordfence has put in some other protections to enforce strong passwords and prevent WordPress from leaking login data.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNDg3IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgODAwIDQ4NyI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23887\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-14.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"487\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-14.png.webp 800w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-14-300x183.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-14-768x468.png.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></p><p>Under Rate Limiting, you\u2019ll see that WF has put some defaults in place but they\u2019re set to Unlimited.&nbsp; You may wish to tweak these.&nbsp; For example, no human should be retrieving hundreds of 404s per minute \u2013 that\u2019s a sign someone is running a script.&nbsp; You could change that to 5 per minute and not risk disappointing any users while still blocking bots.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjc5IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgODAwIDY3OSI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23886\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-13.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"679\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-13.png.webp 800w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-13-300x255.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-13-768x652.png.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></p><p>If you\u2019ve changed anything, be sure to click \u201cSave Changes\u201d at the top.&nbsp; Now click on Scan on the left menu bar.</p><h1>Wordfence Scans</h1><p>Wordfence also includes a scanner that detects malware, inappropriate file permissions, etc.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNTgwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgODAwIDU4MCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23895\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-21.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"580\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-21.png.webp 800w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-21-300x218.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-21-768x557.png.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></p><p>Click \u201cStart New Scan\u201d.&nbsp; After running for a bit, here is the report I received:</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjA5IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgODAwIDYwOSI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23894\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-20.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"609\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-20.png.webp 800w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-20-300x228.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-20-768x585.png.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></p><h1>Wordfence 2FA</h1><p>Now click on Login Security in the left menu bar.&nbsp; You\u2019ll receive a tutorial popup about Wordfence 2FA.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iMzQ2IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgODAwIDM0NiI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23893\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-19.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"346\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-19.png.webp 800w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-19-300x130.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-19-768x332.png.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></p><p>This is a great add-on for security, and it\u2019s awesome that it\u2019s now in the free version.&nbsp; Once you dismiss the popup, you\u2019ll see that everything is ready for Wordfence 2FA:</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNjIzIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgODAwIDYyMyI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23897\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-22.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"623\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-22.png.webp 800w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-22-300x234.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-22-768x598.png.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></p><p>In this case, I fired up Microsoft Authenticator on my iPhone, scanned that barcode, and my authenticator app registered it:</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxMjQyIiBoZWlnaHQ9IjQyMiIgdmlld0JveD0iMCAwIDEyNDIgNDIyIj48cmVjdCB3aWR0aD0iMTAwJSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxMDAlIiBmaWxsPSIjY2ZkNGRiIi8+PC9zdmc+\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23898\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/IMG_48B0A268FC3E-1.jpeg.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1242\" height=\"422\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/IMG_48B0A268FC3E-1.jpeg.webp 1242w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/IMG_48B0A268FC3E-1-300x102.jpeg.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/IMG_48B0A268FC3E-1-1024x348.jpeg.webp 1024w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/IMG_48B0A268FC3E-1-768x261.jpeg.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1242px) 100vw, 1242px\"></p><p>I\u2019ll enter the six-digit code in Wordfence (where the 123456 is greyed out) to enable for my account, and then click Activate.&nbsp; WF informs me that I\u2019m now setup.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNDI0IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgODAwIDQyNCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23900\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-25.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"424\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-25.png.webp 800w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-25-300x159.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-25-768x407.png.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></p><p>Going back to Settings, you\u2019ll see that you can enable 2FA on a per-user or per-role basis.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNTU0IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgODAwIDU1NCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23901\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-26.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"554\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-26.png.webp 800w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-26-300x208.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-26-768x532.png.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></p><p>If you click Manage Users, you\u2019re taken to the normal WordPress Users page, but there is now a \u201c2FA Status\u201d column.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iMjAwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgODAwIDIwMCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23903\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-27.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"200\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-27.png.webp 800w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-27-300x75.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-27-768x192.png.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></p><p>Now when I login, after entering my username/password, there\u2019s a second screen that requires 2FA.</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI1MDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNTY4IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNTAwIDU2OCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-23904\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-28.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"568\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-28.png.webp 500w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/wordfence-28-264x300.png.webp 264w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"></p><p>Wrapping Up</p><p>There is much more you can do with Wordfence.&nbsp; The Tools menu, for instance, has a lot of great features that are very handy even besides their security value.&nbsp; I encourage you to read the <a href=\"https://www.wordfence.com/learn/\">Wordfence docs</a> and see how this security tool can help keep your WordPress site safe.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fshields-up-protecting-your-wordpress-site-with-wordfence%2F&amp;t=Shields%20Up%21%20Protecting%20Your%20Wordpress%20Site%20with%20Wordfence\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Shields%20Up%21%20Protecting%20Your%20Wordpress%20Site%20with%20Wordfence&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fshields-up-protecting-your-wordpress-site-with-wordfence%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><span class=\"dpsp-netwo